com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBidg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=6b7cfcc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus</a><br />\n<br />\n係武漢肺炎下全世界停工停市<br />\n經濟衰退已經提早出現<br />\n香港有好多企業都捱唔住要執<br />\n可以預見肺炎之後會有一堆紅色資本進駐香港<br />\n<br />\n而全世界(e.g. 美國 英國 其他陸續有嚟)都會趁呢個機會叫中國賠錢同撤資<br />\n中國一旦真係要賠錢/失去外資香港都唇亡齒寒<br />\n香港一嚟會不斷比各種大白象紅色資本中出<br />\n二嚟各行各業都會大受打擊<br />\n<br />\n除非話比人聽香港都係受害者<br />\n叫人幫我地攞番我地呢幾個月冇左嘅錢<br />\n同比人知道呢單野唔關香港事<br />\n冇錯就係叫美國幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBidg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=6b7cfcc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus</a><br />\n聯署要求美國協助香港追討損失<br />\n全世界排華風氣已經形成<br />\n呢個時候要做嘅係企係西方國家個邊<br />\n如果唔係大灣區等緊大家<br />\n我地而家要做嘅係話比美國聽香港撐你所以你搞中國唔好搞我地<br />\n同比佢知我地想佢點幫我地<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBidg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=6b7cfcc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus</a><br />\n而家要多六萬三千人簽<br />\n每人簽完揾多兩個人簽好快就搞掂<br />\n香港會變大灣區定有望獨立就睇大家了<br />\n<br />\n無成本簽個名唔係唔做啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBidg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=6b7cfcc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus</a>"},{"pid":"3d4ed5f597aadf0acfcd2257b383f05ec35a7e9f","tid":1982532,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:45:17.000Z","msg":"強烈建議美國 &gt;立即&lt; 暫停香港關系法!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1983340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1983340</a>"},{"pid":"ed389a2604cee6533b0cfc7d08f42fbe8b26642b","tid":1982532,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3640a1c055f76778aeafaf4595349b911991c049","tid":1982532,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8608b38be94185250f4a3bee9c21ed629e5d472c","tid":1982532,"uid":41771,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"話移民果班根本只係流於口號嘅應聲蟲，同港共班走狗無分別。<br />\n<br />\n「我要攬炒。」<br />\n共產黨真係同你攬炒就嚇到屎都瀨埋<br />\n<br />\n「手足唔係condom !」<br />\n共產黨打到黎，移民先，手足再見。<br />\n梁凌杰表示: ......<br />\n陳彥琳表示: ......<br />\n周梓樂表示: ......<br />\n被捕手足表示: ......<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命。」<br />\n一國一制，唔光復lu，走先，拜拜。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦表示: ......<br />\n流亡手足表示: ......"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:51:37.000Z","msg":"我只係戥嗰最少七八千個手足唔抵<br />\n後生推曬出去送頭 變曬condom"},{"pid":"14ee8f091935f95c90689204fac81a4b8d8dab5c","tid":1982532,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T19:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655bc81d8664fa7b738d4b335d66aa5eecb64237","tid":1982532,"uid":93072,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c547ea6c00c4e7b29